: #333333;\">Klassiset ripsipidennykset huolto <em>max 1h              </em> <strong>52</strong></span><br data-rich-text-line-break=\"true\" /><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Klassiset ripsipidennykset pikahuolto <em>30min          </em> <strong>30</strong></span><br data-rich-text-line-break=\"true\" /><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Ripsipidennysten poisto                                  <strong>25</strong></span></p>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"customTextColor\":\"#265302\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#265302\" class=\"has-text-color has-text-align-center has-normal-font-size\"><strong>Ehostukset</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">P채iv채meikki                                                <strong>45</strong></span><br data-rich-text-line-break=\"true\" /><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Juhlameikki                                                <strong>62</strong></span><br data-rich-text-line-break=\"true\" /><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Morsiusmeikki <em>(sis. koemeikin sek채 ripsitupsut)          </em><strong>110</strong></span><br data-rich-text-line-break=\"true\" /><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Irtoripsitupsut                                              <strong>+5</strong></span></p>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"customTextColor\":\"#265302\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#265302\" class=\"has-text-color has-text-align-center has-normal-font-size\"><strong>Sokerointi</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><em>Tulossa pian</em></span></p>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Hinnasto', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '27-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-08-07 17:40:53', '2020-08-07 14:40:53', '', 27, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2020/08/07/27-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
